        "title_link": "https://speakerdeck.com/stevepeak/serverless-gives-way-to-storytelling",
        "text": "Dear \"Serverless\", it's time to put you in your place: middle of stack, abstracted away. Developers need to focus on what matters most: business-logic and not the plumbing, deployments, and complexities that plague application development today. Application Storytelling is top-level language that seamlessly connects microservices and functions in a serverless way. Because \"serverless\" is just an abstraction after-all. It's time we amplify development with something we all want: glue code.",
